# # # # # # #     norm_scale: auto-calibrated from gt velocity statistics each forward pass.
# # # # # # #     → norm = max(mean(||v_gt||), 10.0) km/6h, giving dimensionless MSE ∈ [0, ~4]
# # # # # # #     → No manual tuning needed. "l_kin > 0.5 after ep10" threshold is meaningless
# # # # # # #        because norm adjusts automatically as model improves.

# # # # # # #     Using detach() on norm to avoid gradient flowing through the normalization.
# # # # # # #     """
