# # # #     After ep10: well-trained model has heading error ~20° → l_sm ~0.04-0.08

# # # #     No manual threshold needed. l_sm CANNOT exceed 0.5 due to sin² range.
# # # #     The "l_sm > 0.2 stuck" warning is for ep10+, not ep0.

